      Statutory guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Local authority powers to impose restrictions under coronavirus regulations
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Supports the Health Protection (Coronavirus, Restrictions) (England) (No.3) Regulations 2020 that come into force on 18 July 2020. </p>

  </div>
</div>

